WEBVTT

00:00:14.725 --> 00:00:18.487
♪Allergic to fast-food love,
even if it's too naive♪

00:00:18.562 --> 00:00:22.162
♪Just like a hug needs
the right body heat♪

00:00:22.287 --> 00:00:25.437
♪Your “same here” carries
a touch of resolve♪

00:00:25.862 --> 00:00:29.412
♪Pack my bags,
we can set off right now♪

00:00:29.637 --> 00:00:33.112
♪The future is a wondrous,
unknown adventure♪

00:00:33.250 --> 00:00:36.712
♪The journey itself is what truly matters
before the destination♪

00:00:36.787 --> 00:00:40.975
♪Those moments together
are what bind us strongest♪

00:00:41.025 --> 00:00:42.612
♪Connect♪

00:00:42.625 --> 00:00:43.275
♪Let's go!♪

00:00:43.612 --> 00:00:47.137
♪Leave worries behind
in yesterday's sentimentality♪

00:00:47.237 --> 00:00:50.675
♪Today, no dwelling on
negative emotions♪

00:00:50.750 --> 00:00:53.450
♪Tomorrow holds more luck♪

00:00:53.450 --> 00:00:55.262
♪Together we'll create moving melodies♪

00:00:55.262 --> 00:00:58.199
♪The future begins to take shape♪

00:00:59.075 --> 00:01:02.375
=Love in A Secret=
(I Just Want to Drown With You)

00:01:02.675 --> 00:01:06.250
=Episode 17=

00:01:17.240 --> 00:01:18.280
I'm fine.

00:01:31.800 --> 00:01:33.160
Do you need to take a rest, Mr. Lu?

00:01:34.240 --> 00:01:35.760
I'll go back and rest.

00:01:35.960 --> 00:01:37.040
Have the driver pick me up.

00:01:37.040 --> 00:01:37.560
Alright.

00:02:01.520 --> 00:02:02.320
Come.

00:02:02.920 --> 00:02:04.800
Today's Li Zhou's birthday.

00:02:05.000 --> 00:02:06.560
Let's all have a drink together.

00:02:06.560 --> 00:02:07.600
Thank you, Zhu.

00:02:07.840 --> 00:02:09.480
Happy birthday.

00:02:09.480 --> 00:02:10.040
Thank you.

00:02:10.040 --> 00:02:11.280
Drink up.

00:02:17.520 --> 00:02:18.840
Stop drinking.

00:02:19.120 --> 00:02:21.280
You're trying to get yourself drunk.

00:02:21.600 --> 00:02:23.320
Why are you being so naggy?

00:02:23.580 --> 00:02:25.240
What's wrong with me
having a few drinks?

00:02:26.040 --> 00:02:26.640
Come on.

00:02:26.760 --> 00:02:27.800
Drink up.

00:02:27.800 --> 00:02:28.840
Cheers.

00:02:29.800 --> 00:02:31.000
Stop drinking!

00:02:31.840 --> 00:02:32.680
Enjoy?

00:02:33.575 --> 00:02:34.375
Get lost!

00:02:35.400 --> 00:02:37.120
Now!

00:02:41.920 --> 00:02:43.200
Hey.

00:02:46.200 --> 00:02:49.320
Who upset you
that you have to drink this much?

00:02:50.040 --> 00:02:50.840
Ze,

00:02:51.800 --> 00:02:53.920
if something clearly has no outcome,

00:02:54.720 --> 00:02:56.160
would you still do it?

00:02:56.720 --> 00:02:57.680
Of course I would.

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:01.240
See?

00:03:02.640 --> 00:03:04.360
I knew someone out there
was just like me.

00:03:04.920 --> 00:03:06.400
We don't care about the result at all.

00:03:11.680 --> 00:03:12.280
Let's go

00:03:12.640 --> 00:03:13.480
and find Qun.

00:03:17.100 --> 00:03:19.190
You're drinking this much
in the middle of the day.

00:03:19.440 --> 00:03:20.320
Let go.

00:03:21.190 --> 00:03:22.680
Look, I can walk in a straight line.

00:03:22.680 --> 00:03:23.560
You...

00:03:25.880 --> 00:03:26.520
Your shoes.

00:03:33.640 --> 00:03:35.320
(Do you think)

00:03:35.320 --> 00:03:37.280
(we can stay together forever?)

00:03:38.360 --> 00:03:40.080
(What if we break up one day?)

00:03:41.080 --> 00:03:42.520
(So,)

00:03:43.600 --> 00:03:46.000
(are you breaking up with me now?)

00:03:47.200 --> 00:03:48.560
(Have we)

00:03:50.360 --> 00:03:52.520
(ever really been together?)

00:03:52.960 --> 00:03:53.800
See?

00:03:53.800 --> 00:03:55.160
I told you I'm not drunk.

00:03:56.040 --> 00:03:58.087
Are you really going to find
Qun and the others?

00:03:58.400 --> 00:03:59.760
Why not?

00:04:00.720 --> 00:04:03.280
Qun's waiting for me to start the party.

00:04:04.520 --> 00:04:05.400
Let me tell you,

00:04:06.520 --> 00:04:07.880
she even found

00:04:09.400 --> 00:04:10.760
eight male models for me.

00:04:11.320 --> 00:04:12.360
Just listen to me.

00:04:12.360 --> 00:04:13.720
Let's not go, okay?

00:04:13.720 --> 00:04:14.800
Stop nagging.

00:04:26.440 --> 00:04:27.320
Wait.

00:04:28.920 --> 00:04:31.280
Why does that guy look so familiar?

00:04:37.850 --> 00:04:39.730
Isn't this Ye Man?

00:04:40.080 --> 00:04:42.120
My stepmother's son.

00:04:43.320 --> 00:04:45.160
My brother.

00:04:52.080 --> 00:04:53.840
Why are you drunk
in the middle of the day?

00:04:53.840 --> 00:04:54.920
What are you doing here?

00:05:06.080 --> 00:05:07.080
Ze,

00:05:07.960 --> 00:05:11.320
this is between us.

00:05:11.640 --> 00:05:13.080
You don't need to get involved.

00:05:13.640 --> 00:05:14.520
Go home first.

00:05:15.360 --> 00:05:16.160
Are you sure?

00:05:16.800 --> 00:05:19.040
If I leave, then he...

00:05:19.040 --> 00:05:20.780
My sister told you to leave,
so just leave.

00:05:20.920 --> 00:05:22.480
Why so much nonsense?

00:05:23.560 --> 00:05:24.720
Ze,

00:05:25.800 --> 00:05:27.320
listen.

00:05:27.640 --> 00:05:29.240
Qun's upstairs.

00:05:29.320 --> 00:05:30.960
Don't worry about me.

00:05:31.560 --> 00:05:32.560
You can leave first.

00:05:33.760 --> 00:05:34.312
Go home.

00:06:08.120 --> 00:06:09.560
Bye-bye.

00:06:18.720 --> 00:06:20.080
Why are you here?

00:06:21.240 --> 00:06:23.520
Weren't you having lunch with your mom?

00:06:25.160 --> 00:06:26.520
Oh.

00:06:27.480 --> 00:06:30.360
You didn't eat here, did you?

00:06:31.840 --> 00:06:34.000
Perfect. I'll go talk to your mom.

00:06:34.720 --> 00:06:35.320
Come back.

00:06:37.960 --> 00:06:39.320
Whatever you want to say,

00:06:40.120 --> 00:06:41.080
wait until you're sober.

00:06:42.360 --> 00:06:43.560
Why do you get to control me?

00:06:43.640 --> 00:06:45.000
Who do you think you are?

00:06:45.240 --> 00:06:46.440
Mr. Ye,

00:06:46.560 --> 00:06:47.760
the previous order was wrong.

00:06:47.760 --> 00:06:49.120
Could you please help process it?

00:06:49.360 --> 00:06:50.080
Oh.

00:06:51.720 --> 00:06:52.640
A moment.

00:06:55.480 --> 00:06:56.120
Don't move.

00:07:02.840 --> 00:07:03.880
Wrong shoe.

00:07:06.037 --> 00:07:09.012
♪Say I need your love♪

00:07:09.137 --> 00:07:13.612
♪Holding your hand, holding your hand♪

00:07:15.380 --> 00:07:16.940
♪Thinking of nothing at all♪

00:07:16.940 --> 00:07:19.820
♪Time will stop♪

00:07:19.820 --> 00:07:22.820
♪Moonlight will fall across our faces♪

00:07:23.900 --> 00:07:25.212
♪By your side♪

00:07:25.212 --> 00:07:26.525
♪Don't bury everything inside♪

00:07:26.637 --> 00:07:28.900
♪I've never felt♪

00:07:28.900 --> 00:07:32.100
♪My heartbeat race so fast♪

00:07:33.500 --> 00:07:36.100
♪Moonlight rippling on the sea♪

00:07:36.100 --> 00:07:38.500
♪Hiding my love in a wooden boat♪

00:08:12.320 --> 00:08:13.680
Stay here and wait for me.

00:08:14.320 --> 00:08:15.280
Don't run around.

00:08:20.920 --> 00:08:22.840
I don't have a brother.

00:08:25.560 --> 00:08:26.760
Is this Dr. Zhang?

00:08:28.240 --> 00:08:30.160
Send a car to Zijin Grand Hotel.

00:08:31.880 --> 00:08:32.680
Now.

00:08:39.737 --> 00:08:41.847
Drunk in broad daylight?

00:08:42.040 --> 00:08:43.880
Not your dad's
little obedient girl anymore?

00:08:48.360 --> 00:08:49.680
Who's talking?

00:08:54.040 --> 00:08:55.640
It's my stepmother.

00:08:56.360 --> 00:08:58.360
You and your childish trick again.

00:08:58.600 --> 00:08:59.280
Sarcasm,

00:08:59.600 --> 00:09:00.360
mockery,

00:09:00.520 --> 00:09:01.280
provocation.

00:09:01.560 --> 00:09:02.960
You think I'll fall for it?

00:09:05.760 --> 00:09:07.080
Don't get ahead of yourself.

00:09:09.360 --> 00:09:12.040
I went to the private hospital
you often visit.

00:09:13.360 --> 00:09:15.560
So? What are you trying to do?

00:09:16.680 --> 00:09:17.760
What am I trying to do?

00:09:18.200 --> 00:09:20.040
Maybe you should ask yourself
about that.

00:09:20.280 --> 00:09:21.680
Someone your age

00:09:22.160 --> 00:09:23.840
pretending to be pregnant?

00:09:24.880 --> 00:09:26.560
Do you really think they'll believe you?

00:09:29.880 --> 00:09:31.800
I will expose you.

00:09:38.760 --> 00:09:40.080
Your dad won't believe you.

00:09:40.400 --> 00:09:41.920
If I dared to claim I'm pregnant,

00:09:42.120 --> 00:09:43.480
of course I left myself a way out.

00:09:45.720 --> 00:09:47.600
Even if you hadn't come to me today,

00:09:48.480 --> 00:09:49.440
I would've gone to you.

00:09:49.720 --> 00:09:50.680
What are you saying?

00:09:51.720 --> 00:09:53.760
Why are you pushing me so hard?

00:09:53.760 --> 00:09:55.800
Jiaming and I didn't get to
where we are easily.

00:09:56.240 --> 00:09:58.880
I won't allow anyone to tear us apart.

00:09:59.320 --> 00:10:00.400
Especially you.

00:10:01.040 --> 00:10:01.880
Let go!

00:10:10.100 --> 00:10:11.140
Ah!

00:10:28.640 --> 00:10:29.320
Mom.

00:10:29.800 --> 00:10:30.560
Mom.

00:10:31.000 --> 00:10:31.920
Are you okay, Mom?

00:10:33.680 --> 00:10:34.240
Mom.

00:10:34.960 --> 00:10:35.880
Are you okay, Mom?

00:10:35.880 --> 00:10:36.520
Mom.

00:10:59.775 --> 00:11:04.275
♪Bit by bit, I'll forget you♪

00:11:04.500 --> 00:11:08.288
♪Bit by bit, I'll erase the memories♪

00:11:08.463 --> 00:11:12.538
♪From now on,
your image won't linger in my mind♪

00:11:12.538 --> 00:11:16.675
♪Nor will those fragments of the past♪

00:11:16.800 --> 00:11:20.575
♪Days will slowly drift away
like passing clouds♪

00:11:20.575 --> 00:11:24.350
♪I'll learn to stop longing for
what's gone♪

00:11:24.350 --> 00:11:26.625
♪The you in my memories♪

00:11:26.625 --> 00:11:28.638
♪Will fade from clarity♪

00:11:28.638 --> 00:11:34.075
♪How much longer must I wait to♪

00:11:35.638 --> 00:11:41.075
♪Forget you completely?♪